Date of Birth: November 23, 1870<br/>
Birthplace: Fillmore, Utah, USA<br/>
Ordained apostle: April 7, 1918<br/>
Excommunicated: November 12, 1943<br/>
Death: December 31, 1963<br/>
<br/>
Born Nov. 23, 1870, at Fillmore, Millard Co., Utah, to Francis Marion Lyman and Clara Caroline Callister.
Ordained apostle April 7, 1918, by Joseph F. Smith, at age 47; excommunicated Nov. 12, 1943; rebaptized Oct. 27, 1954;
died Dec. 31, 1963, at Salt Lake City, Salt Lake Co., Utah, at age 93.